    "title": "Walk-in Drive Logistics Manager at Gati",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Gati. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Logistics Manager to strengthen our Amritsar-based team.\n\nAbout Gati:\nGati is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gati!",
